United States Map (Equirectangular Projection)

us_states <- ne_states(country = "United States of America",
                       returnclass = "sf") %>%
  filter(name != "Alaska",
         name != "Hawaii")

us_map <- ggplot(us_states) +
  geom_sf() +
  xlab("Longitude") + ylab("Latitude") +
  ggtitle("US Map") +
  theme_pander()
